HEADWORD: Succentor
<hw>Suc"cen*tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL., an
accompanier in singing, fr. <ets>succinere</ets> to sing, to accompany;
<ets>sub</ets> under, after + <ets>canere</ets> to sing.]</ety>
